title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“We observed and heard some screeching (of tires),” she said. [From the New Haven Register, Aug. 22, 2000. Submitted by Mary-Louise Bean, Guilford, Connecticut.]
